name: ASWebAuthenticationSessionWebBrowserSessionHandling
desc: An interface that a session handler implements to handle login requests from an app.

items.name: func begin(ASWebAuthenticationSessionRequest!)
items.desc: Handles the given session request from an app.

items.name: func cancel(ASWebAuthenticationSessionRequest!)
items.desc: Cancels the process of handling the given request.

items.name: class ASWebAuthenticationSessionRequest
items.desc: A login session request that a web browser receives from an app.
